lead_paragraph: Fives, 91.70; Threes, 56.15. Gold is about the same price in Paris and London, and 0.12 per cent. dearer in Hamburg than in London. The Exchange between England and America is nominally 0.67 per cent, in favor of England, leaving a small profit on the importation of gold from the United States.
